git - distributed source control. 

configuration : 

git config --list  : all configurations.
git config core.editor vim : set config parameter in this case setting default editor to vim.



commands :  

git status - check changes .
git add <file_name> 
git add .   == adds all files.
git commit  -a <add> -m <message> "message"


ctrl+shift+Z == exit .

git diff == diff before add to staging area.
git diff --cached == diff between local and stageing area.


git status  == check for modifications
git status -s == '' shorthand  

git checkout <file_name> == revert local changes.